{"tid":1551424,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請幫推，8/9 美領戰術裝扮討論，各手足入","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:15:53.000Z","uid":88169,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9b27cc1252a0f9be186e6dc8dc66cabe38e3cc","tid":1551424,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"我明白今日大家都想尊重場合<br />\n<br />\n但我地打緊仗！ ！ ！ <br />\n<br />\n著住老西又難行 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要係熱到on9</span></span><br />\n其實我地要做啲係令外國知道我地既尊重，又唔可以失去我地全黑既意義。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁既話不如參考我地賭聖，淨係打條tie?大家用自己方法整條tie <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5fQoBk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5fQoBk.jpg&h=64c0083d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一來又行動方便，二來咁特別既舉動可以帶出香港人既創意，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">三來又可以幫下隔離手足打tie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家認同既話可唔可以幫手推，都出門口時帶多幾條tie <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<br />\n原榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"6c16da0ba1eb1868d91f22ec8e0eb8a3a91c99f3","tid":1551424,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2c139e874a465b61080a7131665bde368bb906fc","tid":1551424,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bc5fc6b0af2c6852066b951e1795dd48f8cb15f7","tid":1551424,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:05:55.000Z","msg":"記得全黑口罩唔止係保護自己，係令黑警更難搵到我地既勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b35af0c31c9aba7bc9d609fbdc519ebc5364118","tid":